          "items": false,
          "minItems": 17,
          "maxItems": 17,
          "description": "Required complete verification sequence for CT10 (Default refinement); must contain exactly 17 successful discharge records, one per node from CT10.N01 through CT10.N17 in source order, each satisfying its corresponding concrete node schema."
